{
  "stem": "13874.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know anyone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were men, but some were married and their wives were on the same train, but not with us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know it was unusual.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was, of course-- it had the J, and being Jewish and the visa to go to England.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had to have visas at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my particular visa was restricted to that refugee camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If I wanted to get out of it-- once visiting-- I went Edinburgh to visit a cousin who also was a refugee there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had to get permission from the local police.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know whether it was official or unofficial.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was called the Kitchener Camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think officially it was a refugee-- Jewish refugee camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in the county of Kent near Richborough, not too far from Ramsgate.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was an old British army barrack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's where the name Kitchener Camp came from.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was used for the British Expeditionary Force in World War One.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it fell too-- and there was very little left of it, so it was bought by a Jewish relief organization-- mostly American money-- and restored, mostly with the help of the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "About a thousand, I would say.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't think it was able to hold more.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Primitive.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "More primitive than Dachau.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Toilet facilities, rooms-- rooms, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had no heat in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were army cots.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a refugee-- run by a refugee company.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't even know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- at that time, I didn't care much about anything anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just drifted along wherever I was pushed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was not much interested in my surroundings.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, everybody of course had to help with the maintenance, chores, and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
